<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>406</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Lung-lawmhnak thawngtha kan theih, Jesuh nih an khamh cang, Khi
 thawngtha kha thanh tuah u, Jesuh nih an khamh cang, Ram vialte ah va kal
 law, Khua zakip rili ral tiang, Bawipa thawngtha va chim tuah, Jesuh nih
 an khamh cang.

[V2]
 Tiva tan in va au tuah, Jesuh nih an khamh cang, A hla naimi sin chim
 tuah, Jesuh nih an khamh cang, Tikulh vialte hlasa u, Khat lei tiang
 thanter tuah u, Vawlei ah lunglawmhnak kha, Jesuh nih an khamh cang.

[V3]
 Raldohnak chungah au u, Jesuh nih an khamh cang, Vai-lamtah thihnak
 caah, Jesuh nih an khamh cang, Zaangfahnak kan duh tikah, Nan ruah lai
 khi thawngthabia, Thihnak teinak hla sa u, Jesuh nih an khamh cang.

[V4]
 Vawlei ah au tuah u law, Jesuh nih an khamh cang, Mi vialte
 lunglawmter hna, Jesuh nih an khamh cang, Fing le tlang khua zakip ah,
 Khamhnak bia va chim tuah u, Khi bia teinak hlasaknak Jesuh nih an khamh
 cang.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<title>JESUH NIH AN KHAMH CANG CH406</title>
</song>